00:26:56.010 --> 00:26:57.310
&gt;&gt; Nancy Groce: Okay.

00:26:57.310 --> 00:26:58.610
And that's Irish?

00:26:58.610 --> 00:26:59.910
&gt;&gt; Nate Growler: Yeah,
it's an Irish tune.

00:26:59.910 --> 00:27:01.210
&gt;&gt; Nancy Groce: Okay.

00:27:01.210 --> 00:27:04.910
Are you going to do that and go
into another piece, or just--

00:27:04.910 --> 00:27:07.910
&gt;&gt; Nate Growler: I was thinking
about just doing that one.

00:27:07.910 --> 00:27:09.210
&gt;&gt; Nancy Groce: Okay.

00:27:09.210 --> 00:27:10.510
Okay!

00:27:10.510 --> 00:27:11.810
&gt;&gt; Nate Growler: Okay.

00:27:11.810 --> 00:27:14.110
&gt;&gt; Nancy Groce: Let's hear that.

