00:29:33.050 --> 00:29:34.350
&gt;&gt; Nancy Groce: Lovely.

00:29:34.350 --> 00:29:36.350
Actually, before you sit
down, I have a request.

00:29:36.350 --> 00:29:37.650
Since it's an American fiddle--

00:29:37.650 --> 00:29:38.950
&gt;&gt; Nate Growler: Okay.

